2.5.2 Properties of R (ğœ)
      The time-average autocorrelation function has several useful properties, which are listed
      below:
      1. ğ‘…(0) = âŸ¨ğ‘¥2 (ğ‘¡)âŸ© â‰¥ |ğ‘…(ğœ)|, for all ğœ; that is, an absolute maximum of ğ‘…(ğœ) exists at ğœ = 0.
